  "texts": [
    "DeepGCNs obtain the surrounding nodes of the target node when the dilated rate d is determined by Dilated KNN:",
    "is the neighbor node of the node v. Since GCNs and DeepGCNs are single feature graph convolutional networks, and the graph contains much complex information, so the text features are integrated based on the structural features of the graph to enhance the embedding ability, which meets the diversity of graph information.",
    "In 2021, Li (Yang et al., 2018) proposes HDGCN, which uses a dual channel GCNs structure to jointly model the structure and semantic features of nodes, complementing and enhancing the features of nodes as follows.",
    "Because the semantic features of the nodes contain the semantic features of weakly correlated neighboring nodes, it will become noise data that affects the training effect of the model.",
    "In order to reduce the noise interference on model training and enhance the feature embedding ability, the dual-channel GCN introduces Graph Attention Network and Gateway Recurrent Unit as follows:"
  ]
}